{"tid":681673,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿兒島7日獨遊求意見","createTime":"2018-05-28T08:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T03:39:09.000Z","uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"58afcbd2ac18afb4fe2382604a8c77bccbdf327d","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"黎緊6月會去鹿兒島，酒店book晒，有免費取消可以隨時改既，求去過/將會去既巴打比下意見<br />\n<br />\n酒店安排: 1-3 鹿兒島中央站, 4-5屋久島, 6-7鹿兒島中央站<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 上午11點半，預計去到酒店放低行李再出發應該已經2點左右，市內9行+天文通屋台村等等<br />\nDay 2: 一早去宮崎，鵜戶神宮，日南，青島 (我知行程係會趕，但係為左唔想搬咁多酒店)<br />\nDay 3: 指宿一日遊，砂浴，溫泉，西大山，長崎鼻<br />\nDay 4-5: 屋久島，白谷雲水峽同其他短既路線，繩文杉多數唔去，視乎天氣同自己身體狀況，因為少行山+1個人費事要人救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay 6: 霧島神宮, 神話之里<br />\nDay 7: 仙巖園+櫻島<br />\n<br />\n問題:<br />\n1. Day 1應該有5,6個鐘行, 對行街shopping無咩興趣, 有無咩地方可以去/行<br />\n2. Day 6,7 會唔會太少行程, 有無建議, 據聞櫻島行半日乜都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上述d行程主要睇人d blog, 睇班台仔寫野都係信3成, 成日吹到好大"},{"pid":"2c29873c2a81f1ee5434aa0bb09ab014e09d6391","tid":681673,"uid":41614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"驚冇野做可以去水族館<br />\n有海豚表演睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDolphin port又多野食同手信買<br />\n可以hea到3,4個鐘"},{"pid":"26a60e41e62c3edf7c37a807964fcd3b71d33c2a","tid":681673,"uid":126165,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"如果你搭hx嗰班機<br />\nlast day 只可以去到桜島"},{"pid":"1d766a19e9503f05ec6c5736e303c84695f91ad3","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c29873c2a81f1ee5434aa0bb09ab014e09d6391","tid":681673,"uid":41614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"驚冇野做可以去水族館<br />\n有海豚表演睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDolphin port又多野食同手信買<br />\n可以hea到3,4個鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"考慮下，睇下表演hea下食下野好似幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7169c17c83b3331b551cc0253a9e25c14c905c04","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a60e41e62c3edf7c37a807964fcd3b71d33c2a","tid":681673,"uid":126165,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"如果你搭hx嗰班機<br />\nlast day 只可以去到桜島"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:00:09.000Z","msg":"無寫清楚添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我係8日, 第8日中午機, 所以ignore左, 第7日係full day+住係鹿兒島既"},{"pid":"1e1278d744a0f8774b86c24af6ffdb2409723ec1","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"漏左,<br />\nDay 1: 上午11點半<span style=\"color: red;\">落機</span>，預計去到酒店放低行李再出發應該已經2點左右，市內9行+天文通屋台村等等"},{"pid":"20265fde1d576d7e9c7aed66e06d41b00546b3c0","tid":681673,"uid":126165,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7169c17c83b3331b551cc0253a9e25c14c905c04","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a60e41e62c3edf7c37a807964fcd3b71d33c2a","tid":681673,"uid":126165,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"如果你搭hx嗰班機<br />\nlast day 只可以去到桜島"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:00:09.000Z","msg":"無寫清楚添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我係8日, 第8日中午機, 所以ignore左, 第7日係full day+住係鹿兒島既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"咁得啦，你買張1day pass<br />\n包埋櫻島巡迴巴士"},{"pid":"556d7fa9d5b4e15d7bc12b75eec56c9a10eb3d88","tid":681673,"uid":63870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"早排去左同你行程差唔多，嫌少去埋市內啲博物館囉<br />\n利申冇去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3c93cbafa56aa8b53353941dedd36f0e2e2567","tid":681673,"uid":53506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"仙巖園可以跟觀光巴士1 day pass<br />\n好多市中心景點睇 順便可以夜晚去dolphin port食迴轉壽司"},{"pid":"54f3ef591d3fd57ff00cd80afaa8cdf552ed743d","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"睇左上面講既dolphin port, 1 day pass等等<br />\n其他上面巴打講d散既hea時間地方好似都好近, 點安排好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第1日行埋水族館, dolphin port<br />\n第7日就用盡張welcome cute pass?"},{"pid":"a9a9d32185ed363ebb6bc89fdbc3407e017219e1","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"又或者咁問, 如果我頭3日買南九州張pass, 第1日落機有無咩地方近近地可以去, 如果去熊本兜個圈好似都好趕?<br />\n然後第7日先行櫻島+仙巌園, 水族館+dolphin port"},{"pid":"cd4463dd12e868d773be29b8bf743f505ca121e4","tid":681673,"uid":27162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"6月3去 又係獨遊<br />\n但會上福崗 再玩番落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae09d5e8002c5cbac38a6fdcd7b68be7c6552095","tid":681673,"uid":104992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩去左九州玩左8日，其中一日同你day 2 一樣，不過我係住宮崎。我可以放心同你講，你冇揸車，趕到pk。<br />\n<br />\n我朝早一早出發去左青島，之後要夾巴士時間去日南&amp;鵜戸神宮，好趕。4點幾就尾班巴士。<br />\n<br />\n建議唔去日南，冇咩特別"},{"pid":"ae9f730c59ee7bc97959433adb7b99f4b6cadb7c","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae09d5e8002c5cbac38a6fdcd7b68be7c6552095","tid":681673,"uid":104992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩去左九州玩左8日，其中一日同你day 2 一樣，不過我係住宮崎。我可以放心同你講，你冇揸車，趕到pk。<br />\n<br />\n我朝早一早出發去左青島，之後要夾巴士時間去日南&amp;鵜戸神宮，好趕。4點幾就尾班巴士。<br />\n<br />\n建議唔去日南，冇咩特別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"都係既，我有睇過巴士時間，的確係好趕<br />\n我都見好多人話日南個復活島好人工無咩特別"},{"pid":"de4305212448af7616b059d8ed18c1121a4cd904","tid":681673,"uid":1681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd4463dd12e868d773be29b8bf743f505ca121e4","tid